values:
I mourn my old deleted livejournals.

I should have printed out the entries, or something.

As if my words meant nothing.

[6th and last]
new livejournal.


Today at school they had a memorial for all the soldiers who've died in Iraq. There were hundreds of crosses planted into the grass on the main walkway. Of course there could have been more, if there had been more room. Not even considering the thousands of innocent Iraqi citizens who've died.

Thank you, George Fuck-Up Bush, for starting a war that hasn't changed a single thing besides affecting millions of people in heart-breaking ways.
